Casablanca,ED3l5fWzFio,UgxgagwnjOtdVC55Mix4AaABAg,,@jmh2105,"Even as much as they showed of that great Dueling National Songs ( German & French) instantly makes the hair on my arms stand up... & easily moves me to tear up- in my case... with pride for America, but thru the lens of this  Scene, Showcasing what was at stake in the 2nd World War! By no means a foregone conclusion: Tho Great evil was clearly One of the Combatants! 
i absolutely Dislike the ( attempted ) Blatant manipulation of my emotions: yet, here... What a masterpiece of just That: and i am Gratified at the great conclusion: Almost a salutary experience! And here, in this documentary it is Technically broken down [ Yet None of it's inherent magic is stripped away!], on the contrary- i love to be enlightened as to the various Contributions, 
