Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,UgyXcBbYI5UvzNHWpud4AaABAg.AM1vhYUXWaZAM8SRBCFxcw,UgyXcBbYI5UvzNHWpud4AaABAg,@96Caleb96,"​​@FindingGinaMarieThankyou very much! Atleast i know not to fully rely on it, will try and use landmarks and comms instead!",2025-08-22T20:40:09Z,2025-08-22T21:14:27Z,0,True,,2026-05-11T02:01:59.898595
