Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,UgzTQwvxzbqmQPHpizB4AaABAg.AGI_1P2lBjFAGIwOoh7MNZ,UgzTQwvxzbqmQPHpizB4AaABAg,@FindingGinaMarie,"Wow, Bry, Thank you so much for your very kind words and for subscribing! Please tell your family and friends about us and share our videos. That is what YouTube likes to see and what helps others to find us. We are so grateful for the community we have here! And we loved our time in Morocco. We have a full series that we hope you enjoy. We visited the Sahara Desert and absolutely loved Fes! —Judy
