Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,Ugw7a45JQ1LH6NfVopV4AaABAg.AAWZ6K3mxNBAAa__lERbgk,Ugw7a45JQ1LH6NfVopV4AaABAg,@FindingGinaMarie,I think it is supposed to be more interesting than Casablanca. Although our walking tour guide really didn't recommend anyplace other than Marrakech and Fes except for taking day trips. He specifically discouraged people from visiting Casablanca because of how industrial it is (which seemed to be the general consensus). —Judy,2024-11-08T21:52:37Z,2024-11-08T21:52:37Z,0,True,,2026-05-11T02:02:07.327787
Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,Ugw7a45JQ1LH6NfVopV4AaABAg.AAWZ6K3mxNBAAg6gLrMqW1,Ugw7a45JQ1LH6NfVopV4AaABAg,@dotted8-,"@FindingGinaMarie But you could go visit the replica, Rick’s American Cafe in Casablanca.",2024-11-11T01:26:49Z,2024-11-11T01:26:49Z,0,True,,2026-05-11T02:02:07.327792
Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,Ugw7a45JQ1LH6NfVopV4AaABAg.AAWZ6K3mxNBAAhYRSiFUYB,Ugw7a45JQ1LH6NfVopV4AaABAg,@FindingGinaMarie,"It's surprisingly less kitchy than I would have expected, but we prefer to not move around too much, so being in two cities and a three-day Sahara Desert tour was plenty for us! I don't know that the rest of Casablanca would have lived up to the hype of the movie. —Judy",2024-11-11T14:48:33Z,2024-11-11T14:48:33Z,0,True,,2026-05-11T02:02:07.327800
