Tourism,wFZyNQAIcdE,UgxH7sbPRTGUqFbpsmF4AaABAg,,@truthseeker3962,"Let me get this straight: most of the attractions are panned because tourists resent *other* tourists being there. 
Or else they're knocked for being too commercialized, whereas Mount Rushmore is criticized because there's nothing else there.
Imo, pickpockets are implicitly encouraged by local governments because they ""provide a living"" for locals- i think i actually heard a politician in one of these areas say that in a video. 

American tourists are bad- but so are  European tourists, and those from the Middle East and Asia. 
