“UNBELIEVABLE!!! Article 84 HAS SCORED!!! A long-range legal argument straight into the top corner! The goalkeeper didn’t even dive—he’s appealing to the constitution!”

📢 “Morocco lead 1-0… THREE MONTHS AFTER THE FINAL WHISTLE!!!”

—

“Wait—Article 84 again! It’s running through the defense… no offside, because technically it exists outside time and space!”

⚽ **GOAL!!!**

“2-0! Senegal are protesting, the fans are protesting, even the commentators are protesting—but the goal stands… pending review in 90 business days!”

—

“FINAL MINUTES… and Article 84 is on a hat-trick… this would be historic, or possibly illegal!”

“It shoots—”

⚽ **GOOOAAALLL!!!**

“HAT-TRICK FOR ARTICLE 84!!! A LEGEND OF THE GAME! Zero touches, zero dribbles, but maximum impact in the courtroom!”

—

🎙️ “Full time—well… kind of full time… eventually… Morocco win the AFCON FINAL 3-0… via *administrative excellence*.”

“Senegal players are still on the pitch asking questions… but the answers have been postponed until further notice.”

😂🔥

“Man of the Match? Not Hakimi, not Mane… it’s *Clause 84, subsection B*—what a performance!”

